These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter, roller, tram
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Transport   | roller | helicopter | motorbike | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, colombian, mexican, german
1. the german is on the far right##1
2. the french is on the far left##1
3. the mexican is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | french | mexican | colombian | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
City: hannover, new-york, nizza, colone
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| City   | nizza | hannover | new-york | colone |

